task.summary: Created Django project including LightFM engine
Implemented module for importing places data
Added new dataset from which LightFM model must learn
Implemented user sign up with email (rather than username as it is default)
Implemented login and signup of Users with relative Profile information
Implemented lookup of locations on user registration
Started the development of the process of user profile configuration
Added control on contexts in profile configuration view
Changed index from Bootstrap 3 to Bootstrap 4
Integrated LightFM for getting recommendations and implemented visualization of recommended places
Implemented close places section with filtering (KM, 5 or 10)
Implemented the checkpoint creation for the LightFM model (pickle format) when a new user signs up and implemented a page for showing places selected by the user for each context
Implemented insert of a new rating, so the update of the .csv files (lightfm dataset) and the update of the model using fit_partial (saved as pickle file).
Implemented profile page and the update of it fields
